Q: Create a small calculator which only does ‘+’ or ‘-‘Operations. (Hint: Take three variable inputs with
one being used for the operator)

START 
INPUT Num1
INPUT Num2
INPUT Operator(+ or -)
IF Operator=+ THEN
   SET Ans=Num1+Num2
   PRINT "Ans"
ELSE IF Operator=- THEN
   SET Ans=Num1-Num2
   PRINT "Ans"
ELSE 
   PRINT "Invalid Operator"
END
